Police are hunting a thief who stole an 86-year old woman 's handbag while she prayed at church on Good Friday .
The man posed as a member of the congregation of St James ' church in the Gorton area of Manchester to carry the crime .
As taking one bag , he tried to steal the contents of two other elderly women 's bags before fleeing .
Police have described the incident on April 3 as ` appalling ' and have released e-fit image of the suspected offender .